@startuml sequence_page_load
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Stats Pills - Page Load Flow

actor Visitor
participant "DrawPage" as DP
participant "api.ts" as API
participant "Express API" as Server
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Visitor -> DP: Opens draw page
DP -> API: getActiveRaffle()
API -> Server: GET /api/public/active-raffle
Server -> DB: SELECT raffle + participants
DB --> Server: raffle with participants
Server -> Server: Compute totalCount,\nremainingCount
Server --> API: { raffle: { ...totalCount, remainingCount } }
API --> DP: ActiveRafflePublic
DP -> DP: Render StatsPills\n(totalCount, remainingCount,\ndrawnCount)
DP --> Visitor: Page with stat badges

@enduml
